(458, '★ Gut Knife | Night (Field-Tested)', 730, '-9a81dlWLwJ2UUGcVs_nsVtzdOEdtWwKGZZLQHTxDZ7I56KU0Zwwo4NUX4oFJZEHLbXH5ApeO4YmlhxYQknCRvCo04DEVlxkKgpovbSsLQJf1ObcTi5N09K_k4ifqPrxN7LEm1Rd6dd2j6fAodqgjFfn-EpvYzuhINWUdA5rYF-B_FS_wbzn1pDptMjAmCRkunIl-z-DyJdWNjR9', 'Exterior: Field-Tested<br> <br>The most notable feature of a gut knife is the gut hook on the spine of the blade.  Originally popularized as an aid for field dressing game, the gut hook is also effective at  cutting through fibrous materials like rope, webbing, or safety belts with ease. It has individual parts spray-painted solid colors in a night ops color scheme.\n\n<i>It\'s the whisper of the wind... it\'s the bite at your neck</i><br> <br>', '★ Covert Knife', '★ Gut Knife | Night (Field-Tested)', 'Knife,Gut Knife,★,Covert,Field-Tested', 0, '2016-06-16 19:15:45', '8650AC'),
(459, '★ Falchion Knife | Night (Well-Worn)', 730, '-9a81dlWLwJ2UUGcVs_nsVtzdOEdtWwKGZZLQHTxDZ7I56KU0Zwwo4NUX4oFJZEHLbXH5ApeO4YmlhxYQknCRvCo04DEVlxkKgpovbSsLQJf1fLEcjVL49KJh4-0mf7zO6_um25V4dB8teXA54vwxg3tr0VlYjinJo6Re1I_NwyCr1O2w--8g57vvpufy3djsihxsyvcyxWpwUYbANRt2R4', 'Exterior: Well-Worn<br> <br>A modern homage to a falchion sword, this clip point blade has a curved edge. It has individual parts spray-painted solid colors in a night ops color scheme.\n\n<i>It\'s the whisper of the wind... it\'s the bite at your neck</i><br> <br>', '★ Covert Knife', '★ Falchion Knife | Night (Well-Worn)', 'Knife,Falchion Knife,The Falchion Collection,★,Covert,Well-Worn', 0, '2016-06-16 19:15:45', '8650AC'),
(460, '★ M9 Bayonet | Case Hardened (Minimal Wear)', 730, '-9a81dlWLwJ2UUGcVs_nsVtzdOEdtWwKGZZLQHTxDZ7I56KU0Zwwo4NUX4oFJZEHLbXH5ApeO4YmlhxYQknCRvCo04DEVlxkKgpovbSsLQJf3qr3czxb49KzgL-Khsj7OrfUklRd4cJ5ntbN9J7yjRrj_hE6NjqlLNOccgE9MljVqAC8wOzqhJ60tc_BnXZqsigrs3bdmRO-n1gSObDaDdZj', 'Exterior: Minimal Wear<br> <br>This is the M-9 bayonet.  Originally intended to be mounted on a rifle, it is also well suited to close-quarters combat. It has been color case-hardened through the application of wood charcoal at high temperatures.\n\n<i>A little color never hurt anyone</i><br> <br>', '★ Covert Knife', '★ M9 Bayonet | Case Hardened (Minimal Wear)', 'Knife,M9 Bayonet,★,Covert,Minimal Wear', 0, '2016-06-16 19:15:45', '8650AC'),
