(504, 'StatTrak™ Five-SeveN | Urban Hazard (Factory New)', 730, '-9a81dlWLwJ2UUGcVs_nsVtzdOEdtWwKGZZLQHTxDZ7I56KU0Zwwo4NUX4oFJZEHLbXH5ApeO4YmlhxYQknCRvCo04DEVlxkKgposLOzLhRlxfbGTj5X09q_goWYkuHxPYTEhGlQ5vp5i_PA54jKhF2zowcDPzixc9OLdgM4aF7WrlO9l7-5hJa_uM7MyCBruyMit3iMmBW1iBwdOOVngvWcT0LeWfIFPrcKKw', 'Exterior: Factory New<br> <br><span style=color:#99ccff;>This item features StatTrak™ technology, which tracks certain statistics when equipped by its owner.<br></span> <br><span style=color:#CF6A32;>This item tracks Confirmed Kills.<br></span> <br>Highly accurate and armor-piercing, the pricy Five-Seven is a slow-loader that compensates with a generous 20-round magazine and forgiving recoil. It has been custom painted with urban camo and red accents.\n\n<i>Every year, Booth gathers the worlds foremost designer gunsmiths to show off their latest designs</i><br> <br><span style=color:#9da1a9;>The Vanguard Collection<br></span> <br>', 'StatTrak™ Mil-Spec Grade Pistol', 'StatTrak™ Five-SeveN | Urban Hazard (Factory New)', 'Pistol,Five-SeveN,The Vanguard Collection,StatTrak™,Mil-Spec Grade,Factory New', 0, '2016-09-27 23:59:11', 'CF6A32'),
(505, 'MP7 | Army Recon (Field-Tested)', 730, '-9a81dlWLwJ2UUGcVs_nsVtzdOEdtWwKGZZLQHTxDZ7I56KU0Zwwo4NUX4oFJZEHLbXH5ApeO4YmlhxYQknCRvCo04DEVlxkKgpou6ryFBRw7ODYYzxb092kmZm0mvLwOq7cqWdQ-sJ0xOqQpYitjgftrUZkZGH7cIGQdVNtZl2F_Vm2krztjJHo7siamyRjs3U8pSGKd9XfyE0', 'Exterior: Field-Tested<br> <br>Versatile but expensive, the German-made MP7 SMG is the perfect choice for high-impact close-range combat. It has been spray-painted freehand with short, thick lines in contrasting colors.\n\n<i>Perfect for the insurgent on the go</i><br> <br><span style=color:#9da1a9;>The Safehouse Collection<br></span> <br>', 'Consumer Grade SMG', 'MP7 | Army Recon (Field-Tested)', 'SMG,MP7,The Safehouse Collection,Normal,Consumer Grade,Field-Tested', 0, '2016-09-27 23:59:11', 'D2D2D2'),
(506, 'MAC-10 | Silver (Factory New)', 730, '-9a81dlWLwJ2UUGcVs_nsVtzdOEdtWwKGZZLQHTxDZ7I56KU0Zwwo4NUX4oFJZEHLbXH5ApeO4YmlhxYQknCRvCo04DEVlxkKgpou7umeldf0v33YjRO-tmkq4yCkP_gDLfQhGxUpsQkjujAo9-k2FDk_UNsZWmiINTGdwVqYwnW_lC7wr-71J656cmcmnF9-n51yj-wIGQ', 'Exterior: Factory New<br> <br>Essentially a box that bullets come out of, the MAC-10 SMG boasts a high rate of fire, with poor spread accuracy and high recoil as trade-offs. It has been painted with a chrome base coat and candied in transparent silver anodized effect paint.\n\n<i>There is beauty in simplicity - Franz Kriegeld, Phoenix Tactician</i><br> <br><span style=color:#9da1a9;>The Bank Collection<br></span> <br>', 'Industrial Grade SMG', 'MAC-10 | Silver (Factory New)', 'SMG,MAC-10,The Bank Collection,Normal,Industrial Grade,Factory New', 0, '2016-09-27 23:59:11', 'D2D2D2');
